Go to Smart Architecture >> All ACLs
In this tab you can see all the predefined ACL

----------------------------------------------------------------
To Add user-defined ACL click +
in the Match Expression add this Vendor-Class Identifier
match if option vendor-class-identifier = "Cisco AP c1240";                //this will specify the vendor is matching to Cisco APc1240



To Check the Vendor-Class of the device go to CLI of the DHCP Server
# tcpdump -i em1 -vv | grep Vendor-Class
